                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-677" type="surname" value="CHURCHILL"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420613-name-677" type="given" value="FRANCIS"></interp>FRANCIS CHURCHILL</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Southampton-court, Tottenham Court-road. The prisoner used to be in my room, where I slept—I placed 18<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. in copper in a cloth in my room, in a box, which I locked—the prisoner saw it—on the 17th of May I got up in the morning, and left the prisoner in bed—he said, "Don't lock me in"—I said I would return, and in about an hour I returned, and found my door half open, the box broken open, and the money gone—it was the prisoner's business to have come back and staid with me—no money has been found.</p>
